description: This file 'plugin_main.h' is a C header file defining APIs for a COSA Library plugin. It includes macro definitions, function declarations for initialization, support checks, and unloading, along with license and copyright notices.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the COSA plugin with maximum supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specific object, identified by name, is supported.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Performs cleanup and unloads the plugin.
